            "title": "韓股高收0.32%　連升4日",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南韓股市靠穩，首爾綜合指數收報2637點，升8點，升幅0.32%，連升4日，再創近1個月新高。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"韓股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250211_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"韓股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250211_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">韓股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
