            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">台灣股市高收。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">加權指數收報22377點，升416點，升幅1.9%。</p>\n</div>",
